01:36:11,745 --> 01:36:14,550
It's a subject matter that needs to be discussed.

839
01:36:15,236 --> 01:36:18,618
The statistics that were given are actual statistics.

840
01:36:18,838 --> 01:36:21,059
You can't get away because they're not lying.

841
01:36:21,899 --> 01:36:37,807
