842
01:36:38,487 --> 01:36:45,333
They're doing more work because they have to deal with undocumented illegals over and beyond their regular course.

843
01:36:46,214 --> 01:36:48,556
Now, are all of them bad people?

844
01:36:48,696 --> 01:36:49,637
Absolutely not.

845
01:36:49,897 --> 01:36:52,119
Do they deserve a fair shot?

846
01:36:52,239 --> 01:36:52,900
Absolutely.

847
01:36:54,298 --> 01:36:59,503
And if they have to have some political intervention, which is taking place right now in Washington, so be it.

848
01:37:00,324 --> 01:37:01,765
But the fact of the matter is this.

849
01:37:02,566 --> 01:37:15,198
I stand here and I resent the fact that anyone, any seven of you or anyone in this audience, who wants to turn around and say, because I was born white, that I am privileged, that is false, that is wrong, and that is a lie.

850
01:37:15,519 --> 01:37:17,641
