1016
01:52:08,992 --> 01:52:11,714
I've seen so many car accidents outside my window as I'm typing.

1017
01:52:12,174 --> 01:52:17,437
I saw a guy in the street on Salem Street, and I've had to get two restraining orders on people.

1018
01:52:17,817 --> 01:52:20,839
The police didn't help me at all, not the fine good men and women.

1019
01:52:21,360 --> 01:52:27,405
But for political reasons, I had to go get a four-year restraining order on someone who was coming to my home and threatening me.

1020
01:52:28,006 --> 01:52:47,023
So no, when I read in the paper that an MBTA cop doesn't get a breathalyzer, but eight days later, I'm in criminal court because people are lying about me, or if I get assaulted outside of these doors by someone in this room, and the police don't do a proper investigation, but I have to spend thousands of dollars in court to find out that people lied about me.

1021
01:52:47,623 --> 01:52:49,004
No, this isn't a safe city.

1022
01:52:49,365 --> 01:52:51,406
You have the haves and the have-nots.

1023
01:52:51,727 --> 01:52:59,253
And if you're outspoken, as I am, and you try to better your city, which I have tried to do, I have been beaten, I've been harassed, and I've been threatened.

1024
01:52:59,853 --> 01:53:01,995
And Police Chief Sacco has not helped me at all.

1025
01:53:02,456 --> 01:53:04,157
So shame on you, Police Chief Sacco.

1026
01:53:04,237 --> 01:53:07,900
I'm a victim, and you hung me out to dry, Chief.

1027
01:53:08,280 --> 01:53:10,863
And your own son didn't even get a breathalyzer.

1028
01:53:19,960 --> 01:53:20,321
Thank you.

